Description:
A BeGreen é uma empresa de agrotecnologia dedicada a revolucionar o mercado nacional com soluções sustentáveis que impactam positivamente o Brasil e o mundo. 

Nossa missão é revolucionar esse mercado:

 Reduzindo a pegada de carbono e gases de efeito estufa;
 Tornando o produtor brasileiro independente dos insumos importados;
 Investindo em ciência e tecnologia agrícola;
 Usando energia limpa e renovável;
 Promovendo segurança alimentar no Brasil.

O futuro do agronegócio é verde, e na BeGreen estamos preparados para liderar essa transformação. 

Venha fazer parte dessa mudança e esteja à frente das principais tendências globais do setor.  

Seja um parceiro BeGreen!

Oushangyuan Process & Equipment Intelligent Co., founded in 2011, located in Tianjin Shuanggang Industrial Park, which is a National High-tech Enterprise integrates the whole EPC process, whole value chain and the “one-stop” comprehensive service of R&D, consulting, technology, design, procurement, construction, equipment manufacturing, start-up, operation, maintenance, training, etc. Oushangyuan is deeply engaged in starch, starch glucose, biological fermentation, chemical and environmental protection project, as well as the engineering design and software programming of the automatic control production line, installation, commissioning of the project, equipment and instruments. So far, Oushangyuan Co. had participated in and implemented the following projects (parts) in China: 
1.Corn starch project: more than 10 million tons; 
2.Liquid glucose / maltose project: more than 3 million tons; 
3.Maltodextrin project: more than 0.5 million tons;
4.DMH / DAH project: more than 1 million tons;
5.Fructose project: more than 1.3 million tons;
6.Functional sugar / mycose / allulose project: more than 200,000 tons;
7.Lactic acid project: more than 250,000 tons;
All the customers are the most powerful and influential manufacturers in China. 
Oushangyuan Co. has a group of technical experts in different yield and technicians with strong abilitIes in product R&D and process design. Continuous accumulate and innovate on the basis of automation services experience in starch, starch glucose and biological fermentation industry to make the company gain lots of outstanding achievements in the application & development of automatic control system, production technology improvement, R&D of the advanced equipment, etc. which is widely applied in production of sugar cane, corn starch, maltodextrin (MDP), glucose, DMH, DAH, fructose (HFCS), crystalline fructose, sorbitol, allulose, mycose, lysine, sodium gluconate, lactic acid, and other organic acids production line.

GENEZIS Trade Germany GmbH is a 100% subsidiary of NITROGENMÜVEK ZRT, who is the sole producer of nitrogen-based fertilisers in Hungary and one of the largest in Central Europe. The Company’s products are largely sold to agricultural producers, both in Hungary and in neighbouring countries. While Hungary has historically been the Company’s principal market, export sales represent a significant business opportunity that the Company aims to explore with an expanding presence and a growing sales team. To accompany and supplement its principal fertiliser business the Company launched in 2014 three new business lines to offer a full range of agricultural inputs to end-users. The scope of such additional activities includes the purchase and sale of seeds, grains and pesticides.   

The Company’s principal strengths include: 
	• Domestic and regional leader, with limited competition; 
	• Product diversity and quality; 
	• Modern plants and very advanced technology; 
	• Unique domestic distribution network; 
	• Stable and diversified business that is resistant to economic downturns and resilient to economic cycles; 
	• Dynamic, experienced and highly focused management team with a proven track record.

www.nitrogenmuvek.hu

As Agrikem;
We believe that only an approach based on science in plant health can provide long-term solutions. With this belief, we base our work and vision on the world's developing scientific data.

We aim to contribute to the production of healthier products with increasing consumer awareness for a more livable world. For this, our main goal is to offer and disseminate plant protection products suitable for nature and environmentally friendly integrated control programs.
